# ORIG TITLE    Russia buries oscar-nominated director Todorovsky . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Oscar nominated filmmaker Pyotr Todorovsky has been buried in Moscow. The Russian director made more than 20 films. He also wrote many of the scores. One of his movies is Intergirl (1989), based on the then-controversial subject of prostitution. Todorovsky died on Friday. He was 87. 
